  "description": "Allpass resonator at maximum (resoMix=0.95): the quasi-Karplus-Strong effect fully engaged. Instantaneous attack (0.001s) means the allpass resonator begins ringing before the additive partials bloom — you hear the physical cavity first, then spectral overtones emerge from within it. Phi constant at depth 2 (3/2 = 1.5, a perfect fifth above fundamental) so the resonator cavity reinforces a musically consonant interval. Short decay, low sustain: this is a pluck, not a pad. The Nautilus shell as a resonating body struck once and left to decay. velBright=0.9 makes soft plucks warm and dark, hard plucks crystalline.",
